Title: The Orchestra

Created By: Jeraldin Espana

The Orchestra is a 2D narrative driven game where the player auditions for their spot in an Orchestra. 
In this game you are able to meet characters representative of different parts of the world and a bit of their stories.
This game requires Unity’s 6000.0.24f1 editor version as well as a computer.
